Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背負著和雷歐帕羅特一起同Nerval戰鬥的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然這樣說你也不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 總之先帶我們參觀一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參觀下雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你見王的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是穗乃香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就把你帶到雷歐帕羅特那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開車的話由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來終於可以著手對這個大東西進行搜查了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 下來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種謎團都太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮太多的話又會暈頭轉向了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克羅比先生也是需要鐵成分的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:44.95,EDTITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(405,290)}{\fs45}{\fad(500,500)}通往黑暗的誘惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到連庫桑齊貝都會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陰險的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在絕對是在和Nerval一起想辦法報復我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我也不再是以前的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定可以達到自我實現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們回家辦婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊 從哪進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絨球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怦怦跳絨球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們成為朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是煞風景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼感覺那麼潮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣真渾濁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼儀式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝作不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不脫鞋子就進別人屋子裡 怎麼這麼沒常識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 我是看這裡太荒涼了 想著能為你做點什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間是基於我洗練過的美學…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也算是洗練的話 禁閉室都算是高級賓館了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以和雷歐帕羅特對話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是風音大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 就不再繼續和你瞎扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做獅子堂風音 妹妹一直以來受你的照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂 枯葉的姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是高嶺 秋葉的二姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的愛爾·蘇爾 是蘇爾家的當家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那裡的是最小的妹妹小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊絨球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}（你…對我做什麼啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單刀直入的說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了設置與Nerval戰鬥時的戰略據點而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個殖民地…也就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將進入獅子堂評議會的管理圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擅自在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會被任何人管理的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 和Nerval的戰鬥是我自己的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道什麼評議會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂評議會？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經叛亂軍…可以這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那…那傢伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這這這…這…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網上購物的集點卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效期限是五十年前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁紙的捲筒 寶特瓶的蓋子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這些垃圾是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 這個也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼啊 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪 啪 啵 啵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跳 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再糟蹋我的崇高的收藏品的話…嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們成為朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止吧！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些沒常識的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…關於智能殖民地我有事要問…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事去問Nerval
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 光這麼單方面的一個勁的說也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 之後再去說服雷歐帕羅特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之必須決定據點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如Enigma之類的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖地Enigma
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊 很有象徵性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enigma？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡不允許進入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 必須得考慮到你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香 你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去安裝部件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也可以一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡閒著也不是辦法 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:07:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（控制室站前 控制室站前到達 請注意不要落下東西）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉 好久沒有湧出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能進去泡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次湧出來的時候進去泡了 慶祝勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還是吉祥物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也算是將Nerval的首次威脅擊退了呢 進去泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 這不挺好嗎 下山同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 神風伊月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你以為你沒暴露嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 為什麼溫泉會在雷歐帕羅特裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球的事 還有什麼評議會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你想從哪裡開始問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起因是距現在半個世紀前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirkwood外延部的宙域以試驗為目的創造了殖民地群
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了人類更為合理的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭載了可以自主思考 自主調整環境的人工智能的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是智能殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智能殖民地？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中心第一號島嶼的代號便是Nerval
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因運行良好 以其數據為基礎又建造了數個智能殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 人口超過一百萬人時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nerval背叛了人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智能腦們將與外部的交流全部遮斷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將居民囚禁起來 並進行支配
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被囚禁的居民與人工智能進行的內戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「Nerval事變」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙生活的人類拚命要隱藏的歷史的真實哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nerval事變？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 與壓迫者Nerval戰鬥的叛亂軍就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在被稱為獅子堂評議會和雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑借他和獅子堂評議會的英雄般的活躍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出了生存下來的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然破壞了事件的組織 罪魁禍首的Nerval卻逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待捲土重來的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量信徒 「Nervalist」潛伏在人類社會中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「從再次出現的Nerval手中保護人類」這就是獅子堂家的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為主導開發智能殖民地的 正是獅子堂財團
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼 我要和雷歐帕羅特一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶「穿越宇宙的少女」是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特裡還真是超絕的大自然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷卻裝置被奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊 那個奇怪的怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便形容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個生物我可是好好的給取了名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學名「庫勞克迪利亞斯·雷歐帕羅達斯」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑熊貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別四捨五入的叫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你連大腦都是乾巴巴的 枯葉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰乾巴巴的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個庫勞克迪利亞斯·雷歐帕羅達斯怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿走了黃金寶玉的冷卻裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 將那個部件給…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？？？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼慌張幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會使反物質爐爆發性的臨界爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆發性的臨界爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點取回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做啊 那個黑熊貓去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它喜歡冷的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是在熱循環系統的冷卻管道裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是哪裡？ 有地圖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有 丟掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂人生啊 就是沒有地圖的旅途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄丟了就直說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 有軌電車經過的車站裡有個「圖書館站前」喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館裡會不會有什麼線索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵 你還真注意到了一個好地方呢 作為煮芋頭來說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了煮芋頭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館站前 圖書館站前到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像會有妖怪出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪？妖怪就是在拚命守護著金銀財寶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是童話看多了 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然妖怪什麼的 是我們靈異科的專門領域
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而目擊報告 超過九成的是誤報 差額 錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的數據可以證明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛才有怪獸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還被襲擊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上也有用科學和道理解釋不清的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 伊月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡找嗎 Crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之分開找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有年代的裝訂本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？哪個哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無家可歸的人工智能\N我的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前開始就為所欲為呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來「Nerval事件」是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼她會知道呢 穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了~~！！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 奈美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風音大人和秋葉大人因為有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 和我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我是誰也不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 又搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無頭妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月 這好像是歸我們管的事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏魯 那麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 中大獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個甲冑是真正的惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那剛才 不說都是誤報 差額 錯覺嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該有的總會有的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ICP交戰狀態成立 反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 烏魯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:13:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖水噴灑器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疊加超聲波
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超聲波停止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將古今中外的一切咒文 教典的聲音壓縮後的產物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 對我們說說你在這的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與靈進行意識溝通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「把頭還來」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發…發飆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這案件真是搞不懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄的也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果拿不到地圖的話就會爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚卡的…怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「地圖 想要嗎？」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「跟我來」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我們跟去…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「在這裡找我的頭」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「找到了就給你們地圖」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很拽的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 只能做了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月 已經在做自己選擇的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那個…伊月你為什麼要進靈異科呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡鬼怪之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴過你我的雙親都失蹤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道「神秘失蹤事件」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(378,360)}{\fs20}Terra abduction
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺…豬？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:16:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一晚上就有數十萬的人消失的大規模失蹤事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的了 連ICP都無法認定這個事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…當時就處在雙親所捲入的現場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒有一個人相信我說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察也是 政府機關的人也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我只有五歲 說出的這些也相當荒誕無稽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想…證明那個實際發生過的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 在被當作特殊學生的接受教育後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了靈異科的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申請加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊 伊月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這些比起來我什麼…什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 找到頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應爐的暴走已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 那麼得趕快了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 快點安上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在考慮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不合適
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成佛之前給我地圖…地圖！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地圖GET
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 惡靈先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的某處有那個怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是冷卻裝置！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要推下去啊啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要行動的話早說啊 穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 如果沒有這個的話 你們也會死掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然之間做什麼啊 這個小不點熊貓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊貓媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了…生氣了…生氣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章…章魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪也出來了 還有怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特的裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…是什麼世界啊！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mission Complete
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱷魚之外還有一個章魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章魚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 發現新品種了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 章魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.09,0:19:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 命名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學名為「雷歐帕羅塔·奧庫特帕塔」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐熊貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過別隨便四捨五入的叫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我是原ICP特殊靈異事件專屬搜查科的神風伊月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 啊！！你們！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才將房間弄成原來的樣子 你們太沒常識了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 到底是誰沒常識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我總是一味的焦急 只考慮了自己事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 要變的和別人無所不談的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須踏踏實實的建立起信賴關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 毫無保留的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月 去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先應該幫助雷歐帕羅特打掃房間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？穗乃香哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心動動物圖鑒的第三冊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…第二冊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校正設施和未確認構造物之間的互相扭打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.88,0:21:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好的報告書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 不勝榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅沒能逮捕神風伊月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還將用市民的苛稅製造的QT-Arms嚴重毀壞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆的命也差不多到時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去等候處分  退下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 不是爆炸頭 是天生的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們走路不長眼睛啊 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 走路眼睛要長哪啊 你這個醉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們非要給你這種醉漢道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也許連明天的太陽都見不到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:21:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Fu~」的一下啊 生命會「Fu~」的一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風中蠟燭「Fu~」的一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界太TM假了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們要遭到這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是神風伊月…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蜜 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.90,0:24:14.80,EDTITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(555,310)}Q速無限
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞 破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.46,0:24:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連靈魂都不剩下的壓倒性的破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.98,0:24:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羈絆 愛 連未來都要燒盡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.06,0:24:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕望的業火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳凰在火焰的灰燼中復生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:17.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空を駆ける 自由に優雅に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:21.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩にも心にも少女は翼を持つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生まれ落ちた世界は美しい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:28.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神さえ支配できない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:35.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望(ゆめ)は暗黒に埋められた星で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:39.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見てるだけじゃ輝かず
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:43.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私のカラダは宇宙船となり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:46.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考の大気を昇って果てそう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:54.33,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平穏に甘んじたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:02:01.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂(ハート)がバグ起こす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:05.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇあなたのロケットで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:08.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌道修正してくださる?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:12.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繋がって確かめ合う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:18.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私たちアンドロイドじゃないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:21.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虹を掛ける 明日へ誰かへ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:25.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願えば届くと少しづつ信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:29.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進んでゆく世界は果て無い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:33.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神にさえ破壊できない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:38.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人が抱えた罪もいつか消えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:17.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由地 優雅的在天空翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:21.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女們在肩上和心中都有一雙翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們所誕生的這個世界如此美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:28.46,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連女神也無法將其支配
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:35.78,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望被埋在黑暗的星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:39.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅看到卻無法閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:43.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們身體化為了宇宙船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:46.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好似要升到了思考的大氣的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:54.33,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果甘於平穩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:02:01.45,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂就會產生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:05.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 可以用你的火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:08.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來修正我的軌道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:12.50,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相連接 確認無誤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:18.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不是機器人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:21.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越彩虹 通向明天 通向誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:25.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果請求就能傳到 開始慢慢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:29.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個正在前進的世界沒有盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:33.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使連神也無法將其破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:38.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人所背負之罪遲早會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:43.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こころが旅立つのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:49.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰もしらない しらない   星の数にときめいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:55.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無敵の好奇心で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.46,0:23:01.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君とのりたい のりたい   過去と未来飛ぶシャトル
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:06.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進む 私たちとめないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:12.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あしたを変えてみるのもいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:21.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進め 迷いから見つかった答えが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:24.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼んだワクワク感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:30.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球でJump！！出会いは銀河の分岐点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:36.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然のいたずらが楽しいんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.17,0:23:41.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いきなりJump！！果て無き宇宙もおともだち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.13,0:23:47.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒険はクセになる そーでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.89,0:23:55.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒険と少女はイコール わかってね！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:01:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:43.85,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與心一起去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:49.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到誰都不知道的繁星而心動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:55.41,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以無敵的好奇心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.46,0:23:01.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要和你一起乘坐那穿越過去與未來的時空梭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:06.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁進吧  誰都無法阻止我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:12.58,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變明天也很不錯的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:21.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁進吧  在迷惘中所找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:24.34,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那答案所呼喚我的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:30.28,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球跳躍!!  而在銀河的分歧點與你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:36.17,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶遇也好 豈不應該更加享受嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.17,0:23:41.93,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻飛躍!! 無邊際的宇宙也是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.13,0:23:47.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過冒險會變成習慣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.89,0:23:55.32,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女的生活就是冒險喲  這你要明白!
